                              Absolutely Bob Brown; or, Bobbed Brown,
                           by Gertrude Stein, printed by Banyon Press, inscribed to CVV (1955)

Includes photographs and photographic postcards of Carlotta and Eugene O'Neill, Tao House, Casa Genotta, and their dog Blemie (1939-1942, undated); 
